snippet.title: SCP: 5K // 0.14 Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description:
The klaxon of a containment breach alarm wakes a lone agent of the FBI's UIU division who finds themselves separated from their unit with no memory as to how they got to this defunct office space. CROW, the lead agent for the UIU operation, struggles to make contact. The worst case scenario has begun. 

UPDATE 0.14 ARRIVES ON MAY 15th
https://store.steampowered.com/app/872670/SCP_5K/

Featuring the voice talents of: 
Rachael Messer as CROW
Justin Pinero as Captain Pinero 
Pavo Schimmer as GOC operative 1 
Daniel Light as GOC Operative 2.

Rachael: https://www.imdb.com/name/nm6005985/
